Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am disappointed, Werewolf Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As am I, Vampire King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You, who fought the Demon Lords\Nand protected this land eons ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now choose to follow such a foolish path.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing more\Nthan desperation to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And nothing has changed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neither have we changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like our forebears, we will battle on\Nuntil we've eradicated the Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Except that I don't wish to fight anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neither with you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's a descendant of the Black Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, I do believe\Nyou've been duped by the Mage Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once harmony is restored,\Nit will mean the end of both Crests and Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As someone who's shed\Nher own blood, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it means leaving\Na peaceful world to my children,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gladly relinquish my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! Such lip service!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That faux-wolf will surely attack soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just get rid of her\Nwhile you have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she's my invited guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking Mother so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We came all this way to meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A storm's brewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, no! I'm all grown up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, sweet puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I assign you the rank of guard, Sir Theo,\Nbut you don't have to join the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a task for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A task? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about I have you do guard duty\Nwhenever I leave the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm here,\Nyou can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Laura Hardry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am somewhat versed in Abjuration Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Helga Piarosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I studied Life Magic at the Mage Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Colleen Messala.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my specialty is alchemy magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've heard the rumors about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You belived once you mastered the basics\Nyou'd learn how to apply them on your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so you switched from major to major.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be quite talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not as much as you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for idle chitchat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're having company tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be attending the welcome banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who will be coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The prince of the small continent\Nof Dartagnia, Lord Milza Kuces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been traveling in secret\Nfor the last five years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and he's stopping by before heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Artuk's neighbor across the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've been on friendly terms\Nsince ancient times, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's an esteemed guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be on your best behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who assassinated\Nthose two archdukes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it goes to show that\Nanybody can still become emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Including you, Lord Milza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To become emperor, one needs geographical\Nadvantages and luck on one's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dartagnia is a small continent,\Neasy to protect but ill-suited for attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should you become emperor, Lord Villar,\NI would be pleased to serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I value aesthetics over ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although, if I became emperor\Nas a result of living a most beautiful life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would gladly accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That sets my mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you had no intention of becoming\Nemperor, Lord Villar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would've taken your Crest\Nback to Dartagnia with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:06:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to cross swords\Nwith you, Lord Milzer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd likely have no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you've fought a wide array of foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you've achieved\Nthe court rank of viscount?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Knight Guard who recently began\Nserving me. His name is Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard many rumors about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think he'd give up his viscount ranking\Nfor a single mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest\Nin those who lack ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how much value Theo sees in Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that young girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, Viscount Lassic David\Nhas begun his conquest of Savis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this Lord Lassic's\Nperformance on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His troops are formidable,\Nand he leads them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villar, you've gained a fine ally,\Nwouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt, he's an ally,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but Lord Lassic is only holding\NSir Theo's court rank for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Lassic is ambitious, but he's even\Noffered up that ambition to Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unthinkable...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who would entrust their ambition to\Nsomeone deprived of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eons ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Lords that emerged in Artuk
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wreaked havoc and destruction for almost\Na decade, until dispersing naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In those days, the citizens of Artuk\Nfortified their villages,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,confronting the Chaos head on\Nin an effort to thwart it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Around this time, a great witch appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A witch? You don't mean a mage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They summon otherworldly projections,\Nsuch as spirits and demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and endow them with wisdom and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are Black Witches who prefer\Nto be connected to the demon world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the witches of Artuk are White Witches,\Nwho swore to never link to the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from the witches,\Npowerful Artists also appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In particular,\Nvampires with their powers of immortality,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the werewolves,\Nwith their powers of regeneration,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are said to have fought\Non equal terms with the Demon Lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Constance family treated them well,\Ngave them complete autonomy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and even signed a pact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The people of Artuk sure are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The people of Systina are too helpless\Nagainst the demon world and the Rossini clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt in my mind that you\Nwill rally your people to make a stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Thanks.\N- Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you,\Ncome to the Audience Hall at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the elder of the White Witches,\NLady Zelma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can just call me Old Hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So are you the new mage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you, being forced to wear\Nyoung Villar's tasteless outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theo. Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In my stead, I want you to head\Nto the Forest of Eternal Darkness at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. What's the nature of our business?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The werewolves have left\Ntheir village en masse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're heading for\Nthe Forest of Eternal Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've spoken with their queen,\Nbut she won't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There hasn't been bad blood like this since\Nthe ancient pact went into effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, that forest is\Nthe vampires' territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't help feeling that\Nsomething terrible is about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, I'm picking up\NLuna and Emma's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you'd show up\Nover a pair of mangy mutts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are your children that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can just bear more\Nif you need them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Return my daughters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I not tell you to come alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going alone from this point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ordering you as your clan leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ion, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So many of our comrades\Nhave lost their lives fighting the Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I will not allow my children\Nto succumb before I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you members of the werewolf clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're emissaries of Villar, the Earl of Artuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We came upon hearing of the feud between\Nthe werewolf clan and the Vampire King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us, what's happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing that concerns you!\NNow get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or else we won't guarantee your survival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Theo Cornaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On behalf of the Earl of Artuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am here to meet with\Nthe Werewolf Queen and the Vampire King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These two are my guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind letting them through?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... the Vampire King?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise,\NI guess you could say I'm his shadow,.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give back my mother and sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emissaries, please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wha–
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you, as the Earl of Artuk's\Nemissaries, we'll do the best that we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just try harming a single hair\Non my mother's or sisters' heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll chase you to the ends of the earth\Nand shred you to pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a thousand times more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just how durable\Nare you werewolves, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a fool...\NI despise people like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure someone like you\Ncould never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see how long you can hold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once you die,\Nit'll be your precious daughters' turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us for our sudden intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I am–\N- No need to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just cut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dmitrie, Vampire King,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,where is your ally,\Nthe Werewolf Queen, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was Yana who summoned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my thing,\Nbut everyone has their own style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that doesn't sit well with you two,\Nfeel free to do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing...\NI'd like you to convey this to Earl Villar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to return to the Dark Ages,\Nrife with the Ultimate Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unless the Crests are shattered,\Nall Lords shall become our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the one who fought\Nthat Ultimate Chaos two thousand years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted was for this twilight era\Nto continue through eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But eventually, the Crests will be fused,\Nand the Emperor's Crest will come into being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if order and harmony are restored,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos will vanish\Nand Artists will lose their power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And for me, it means a permanent ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid to die, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who caused\Nthe Grand Hall Tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm no match...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am not fond of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The queen is in the cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you go now, you can probably save\Nthose she's trying to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have enough power left\Nto regenerate, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I use your Chaos Core,\NI might be able to summon the Demon Lords!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Black Witch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dmitrie's guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to ask questions,\Nstart by telling me who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Theo Cornaro.\NAnd she is Siluca Meletes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're emissaries of Earl Villar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Vampire King just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:15:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After making me do all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I was just a pawn to sacrifice, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Then I'll just do as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Having a man shield you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How I envy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He deflected it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ivy! Vines!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slice it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hurt our mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just puppies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rip you to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you two on another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go after her, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, we're so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take these two outside the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma... Luna...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you'll live strongly and wisely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clara was a great queen,\Nand a strong, kind-hearted mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She loved her clan, her family,\Nand fought gallantly to rescue her daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will carry on her legacy, and her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:20:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two brought my sisters, as well as\Nmy mother's soul, back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The residents of the forest\Npledged their allegiance to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and will come to our aid in times of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm sure they believe\Nthe Vampire King will return one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Governing the Forest of Eternal Darkness,\Nand clearing a path to the demon world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villar is really working us hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though you did accept those tasks,\Ndidn't you, Sir Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Systina is also considered\Npart of the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd learn a thing or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I've heard from Lady Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The White Witch tried to pursue Yana,\Nbut was unable to capture her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Black Witch has terrifying power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I know there are battles\Nthat I cannot afford to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm going to become stronger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, there's no shortage\Nof challenges in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's the fearsome playground\Nleft behind by the Vampire King.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfectly fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For it means that you'll be running me\Ninto the ground once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just teach you\Nproper maids' etiquette?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're still just kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They have the motivation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to go hunt the Chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We want to get stronger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we head north today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.03,0:22:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FOREST OF ETERNAL DARKNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 6:\NMARCHING
